# shadcn/ui Standards and Dependency Management

## Core Principles
- **NEVER install @radix-ui/* or framer-motion dependencies directly**
- **ALWAYS use shadcn/ui components via `npx shadcn@latest add COMPONENT_NAME`**
- **Use existing shadcn/ui components instead of reinventing the wheel**

## Available shadcn/ui Components
Use these components from https://ui.shadcn.com/docs/components:
- Accordion, Alert, Alert Dialog, Aspect Ratio, Avatar, Badge, Breadcrumb
- Button, Calendar, Card, Carousel, Chart, Checkbox, Collapsible
- Combobox, Command, Context Menu, Data Table, Date Picker, Dialog
- Drawer, Dropdown Menu, Hover Card, Input, Input OTP, Label
- Menubar, Navigation Menu, Pagination, Popover, Progress
- Radio Group, Resizable, Scroll-area, Select, Separator, Sheet
- Sidebar, Skeleton, Slider, Sonner, Switch, Table, **Tabs**
- Textarea, Toast, Toggle, Toggle Group, Tooltip, Typography

## Component Usage Guidelines
- **Tabs**: Use shadcn/ui Tabs component instead of custom tab implementations
- **Cards**: Use shadcn/ui Card components for consistent styling
- **Buttons**: Use shadcn/ui Button with appropriate variants
- **Modals**: Use shadcn/ui Dialog or Sheet components
- **Forms**: Use shadcn/ui Input, Label, and form components
- **Navigation**: Use shadcn/ui Navigation Menu or Menubar

## Installation Commands
```bash
# For tabs (which you should use instead of custom implementations)
npx shadcn@latest add tabs

# For other components as needed
npx shadcn@latest add dialog
npx shadcn@latest add sheet
npx shadcn@latest add select
npx shadcn@latest add input
npx shadcn@latest add label
```

## Code Examples
Instead of custom tab implementations like:
```tsx
<div className="flex space-x-1 bg-muted p-1 rounded-lg">
  <Button variant={activeTab === 'vivienda' ? 'default' : 'ghost'}>
    Vivienda
  </Button>
</div>
```

Use shadcn/ui Tabs:
```tsx
import { Tabs, TabsContent, TabsList, TabsTrigger } from "@/components/ui/tabs"

<Tabs defaultValue="vivienda">
  <TabsList>
    <TabsTrigger value="vivienda">Vivienda</TabsTrigger>
    <TabsTrigger value="habitacion">Habitación</TabsTrigger>
  </TabsList>
  <TabsContent value="vivienda">
    {/* Vivienda content */}
  </TabsContent>
  <TabsContent value="habitacion">
    {/* Habitación content */}
  </TabsContent>
</Tabs>
```

## File Structure
- All shadcn/ui components should be in `src/components/ui/`
- Import from `@/components/ui/component-name`
- Follow shadcn/ui naming conventions and patterns
